<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Complaints</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #121212;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: left;
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 500px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background: #1e1e1e;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
        .logo {
            text-align: center;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }
        .logo img {
            width: 150px; /* Adjust the size of your logo */
        }
        .title {
            font-size: 18px;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .details {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding: 10px;
            background: #292929;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display:none;
        }
        .details p {
            margin: 5px 0;
        }
        .highlight {
            color: #4caf50;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .otp-box {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #4caf50;
            background: #292929;
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 5px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 20px;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #bbb;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer a {
            color: #4caf50;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        p{
            color:white!important;
        }

        .details > p{
            text-transform: capitalize;
            margin-top: 7px;
        }
    </style>
    <script>
        function showDetails(){
            const details = document.querySelector(".details");
            if(details){
                details.style.display = "block";
            }
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="logo">
            <img style="width:70px;height:70px" src="<%= marketplaceUrl%>/assets/_images/crygoca-new-logo.jpg" alt="Company Logo">
        </div>
        <h1 style="color: white; font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 30px; font-weight: 700; line-height: 34px; margin-bottom: 0; margin-top: 0;">Complaint Received</h1>


        <p>Dear <strong><%= data.account.username %></strong>,</p>  
        <p>Your complaint <strong># <%= data.complaint.ticketNo %></strong> was received, we will attend to your complaint shortly.</p>  

        <p>For further enquiries, please contact our customer support through the following channels:</p>
        <p><strong>Phone:</strong> +44-273874848838</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:support@crygoca.com">support@crygoca.com</a></p>

        <div class="footer">
            <p>Thank you for choosing <strong>Crygoca</strong>.</p>
            <p>The Crygoca Team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
